high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink on your left.
Pick up the spoon directly to the left of the sink.
Walk to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Open the drawer in this counter, and place the spoon in it.
Walk back to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the spoon to the left of the potato.
Walk back to the counter to the right of the fridge.
Place this spoon to the left of the other spoon in this drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place two spoons in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the sink.
Pick up the spoon on the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the drawer beside the fridge.
Place the spoon in the drawer and close it.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the spoon on the sink.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the drawer beside the fridge.
Place the spoon in the drawer next to the other spoon and close it.
anns.task_desc: To move two spoons from the sink to the drawer next to the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and then turn to your left to face the counter
Pick up a spoon from the counter
Turn around and then maneuver to face the counter to the right of the fridge
Open the drawer and put the spoon in it
Turn around and go back to where you were standing before
Pick up another spoon from the counter
Head back to the spot next to the fridge
Put the second spoon in the drawer too
anns.task_desc: Put two spoons in the kitchen drawer
